      <p class="- topic/p ">You can register your org for Power Upgrade Program to auto-upgrade Power managed packages.
         Power Upgrade Program supports upgrading from the Spring '18 release or later to the latest
         major release (n) or previous two major releases (n–1 or n– 2). </p>
